snippet.textDisplay:
Sometimes, i realize, that the only thing that combines the two otherwise arch rivals ( Pakistan And India) is this Beautiful Music sung from across the two sides, two boundaries, two nations.......... But one Soul, The soul of Music.... Enjoy this magical moment of unification for tomorrow we go to war again, we go to each others throat again, we go separate ways again....
Long Live Music.
